{"tid":1551431,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"人黎呀！中環站賓賓人數多過我地好多呀！","createTime":"2019-09-08T04:06:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T06:45:54.000Z","uid":183438,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"45b205cc360599d9d37c53c39fb31411ed6d5141","tid":1551431,"uid":183438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:06:29.000Z","msg":"唔係幾見到示威者！反而好多賓賓！人黎呀，等陣遮打花園比賓賓佔據啦<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1MXGvim.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1MXGvim.png&h=6126bf05&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"387762d524e8920cbf683ab18297eb1383eaf1c6","tid":1551431,"uid":9049,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:07:18.000Z","msg":"「懷疑有組織發佈大量fake news想搞散場抗爭」<br />\n做人要有公關！文宣多一個就好多！連儂牆要人！<br />\n<br />\n今日 下午 美國領事館 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>衛城長久戰，生活中抗爭；<br />\n拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗；</strong><br />\n<br />\n每日任務：<br />\n1. 抵制「邪惡」「無良」的商戶，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶、減少八達通<br />\n2. 安全情況下跳閘，免費搭港鐵<br />\n3. 夜晚十點吶喊！！！<br />\n4. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n4. 每日一post，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest #Chinazi<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests <br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprspe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=bb8d7539\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n5. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n6. 保持獨立思考，分析能力level up，抵抗fake news/ rumour ，五毛分化post<br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 做孝子救港，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股<br />\n2. MPF都買美股<br />\n3. 搵多幾個人參與<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.08"},{"pid":"545e6bc19c72e432269b28eefb167b12b74cd579","tid":1551431,"uid":275607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:11:47.000Z","msg":"中環站中，我都係見到賓賓多過自己友<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eb2588a26c9912e988e7ce280856c588c14a3e2","tid":1551431,"uid":183438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:30:01.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"da645b05cb5034152f5b2bdf82b18e9c549caa1d","tid":1551431,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:30:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"063b6f5ae6e772aa363a5552105e4c1c675d364d","tid":1551431,"uid":19728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:31:05.000Z","msg":"而家先十二點半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"105783980d3ad6e50e784a983fb355844b6e882b","tid":1551431,"uid":311734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:31:15.000Z","msg":"呢個真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95517b38695941e3f28f5e0e0661c65fe572bd9b","tid":1551431,"uid":54832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:37:21.000Z","msg":"你睇你地班廢青<br />\n人地賓賓無分季節 天氣<br />\n每年每月每個星期日都出來靜坐撑香港人<br />\n個個都帶埋地席野食作長期抗爭<br />\n你地點可以唔出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59b01ce3dc00c0f59fa35479bb9ae6480b19a5df","tid":1551431,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:38:07.000Z","msg":"幾點呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"0aa7938603a84a0e25c846c76573fcc2d343f4f0","tid":1551431,"uid":264192,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:40:35.000Z","msg":"9月8號有一個大原則，就係<br />\n突顯香港人對待美領嘅尊重<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋對待中聯辦嘅蔑視<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兩者要做到高下立見<br />\n<br />\n1. 戴頭盔豬咀，經過美領時除帽致意<br />\n2. 無上gear嘅全部著曬西裝<br />\n3. 一片美國旗海<br />\n4. 個個都要識唱美國國歌<br />\n5. 唔識唱嘅肅立就得，唔好睇手機"},{"pid":"cd9a19b3c7cadfd3d4cd94728776b96e4fe115c3","tid":1551431,"uid":118787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:41:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8fd632e1e3940c30a0f21517147010bac4d6da8","tid":1551431,"uid":183438,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:42:59.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"07278b6c1ba5f42d278a3fb4a9f394d8e9312044","tid":1551431,"uid":74929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:44:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W16DxAR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW16DxAR.jpg&h=6b663e35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B1mTkZ7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB1mTkZ7.jpg&h=106f1e65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/08/121821_334341e1fd8cd0795176f952631cddf0.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F08%2F121821_334341e1fd8cd0795176f952631cddf0.jpeg&h=0ace8822&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Gvdmuh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Gvdmuh.jpg&h=88cf1465&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>美國國歌唔同大陸國歌唔需要一定跟著唱 大部份場合只有一個領唱者</ins> <br />\n<br />\n唔識唱嘅話單手放心口就得<br />\n唔想放喺心口嘅話面向國旗都可<br />\n<br />\n記得除帽 口罩要帶保護返自己<br />\n美國佬好隨和其實着咩都冇所謂<br />\n<ins>最緊要有人到有心最重要</ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>今日大家美國領事館見</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n緊急9月8號 weconnect美國重要日子 注意事項<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1551454\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1551454</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"66fdd4ca8cec49fdf30da5986b464dabd7476f6a","t